name: CompliancePackageEntityType
title: CompliancePackageEntityType
description: A container intended to contain sufficient material for more than one use, but grouped or organized to provide individual access to sufficient material for a single use. Often used to ensure that the proper type and amount of material is consumed/expended for each use.
